tp://www.yf-st.com/showImage/1460965707590\" width=\"387\" height=\"240.327\" data-origin-src=\"http://www.yf-st.com/showImage/1460965707590\" data-origin-name=\"图片\" data-origin-size=\"1000,621\">\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle bottom\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right-bottom\"></div>\n</div><p><br></p><p>昨天，逸丰生态养生园迎来一批特殊客人。香港翡翠电视台《吾淑吾食》（Eating WellWith Madam Wong）栏目组在著名主持人黄淑仪带领下，来到逸丰生态养生园拍摄专题节目。节目组的到来表明逸丰生态养生园和莲洲铁皮石斛已蜚声港澳。广东逸丰生态实业有限公司董事长、总经理林伟波热情接待了这些朋友。</p><p><br></p><div class=\"simditor-image\" contenteditable=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"width: 387px; height: 240.327px;\"><img src=\"http://www.yf-st.com/showImage/1460965716402\" width=\"387\" height=\"240.327\" data-origin-src=\"http://www.yf-st.com/showImage/1460965716402\" data-origin-name=\"图片\" data-origin-size=\"1000,621\">\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle bottom\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right-bottom\"></div>\n</div><p><br></p><p>《吾淑吾食》是<a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/388042.htm\" target=\"_blank\">香港电视广播有限公司</a>的一款饮食节目。由<a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/1242597.htm\" target=\"_blank\">黄淑仪</a>、黎志安担任主持，于2013年11月3日起香港时间逢星期日20:00-21:00在<a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/1108978.htm\" target=\"_blank\">翡翠台</a>、<a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/1339311.htm\" target=\"_blank\">高清翡翠台</a>播出，由于节目轻松愉快、贴近民生，开播伊始就成为香港和周边广大观众十分喜爱的一档栏目，收视率很高。</p><p><br></p><p>这次到逸丰生态养生园拍摄的目的是要制做一期美食汤料为主题的节目，据主持人黄淑仪介绍，之所以到逸丰生态养生园拍摄，主要得益于这里出产的莲洲铁皮石斛绿色天然，药效显著，希望给香港朋友推荐一款好的药食同源的食材——莲洲铁皮石斛，更希望观众朋友们观看节目后，对逸丰生态和莲洲铁皮石斛有更深刻的了解，节目播出时间大概在5月中旬。</p><p><br></p><div class=\"simditor-image\" contenteditable=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"width: 387px; height: 240.327px;\"><img src=\"http://www.yf-st.com/showImage/1460965719183\" width=\"387\" height=\"240.327\" data-origin-src=\"http://www.yf-st.com/showImage/1460965719183\" data-origin-name=\"图片\" data-origin-size=\"1000,621\">\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle bottom\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right-bottom\"></div>\n</div><p><br></p><p>拍摄过程中，广东逸丰生态实业有限公司董事长、总经理林伟波向摄制组详细介绍了公司发展和今后规划。希望和翡翠电视台《吾淑吾食》密切合作，制作出更加精美的美食节目。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><br></p>','香港翡翠电视台《吾淑吾食》（Eating WellWith Madam Wong）栏目组在著名主持人黄淑仪带领下，来到逸丰生态养生园拍摄专题节目。'),(23,'集团员工风采','逸丰生态举办冬季趣味运动会辞旧迎新',NULL,NULL,'1461372012245','1460967835303,1460968522176,1460968555316,1460968587160,1460968658597,1460968802549,1460968807565,1460968810705',NULL,'2016-04-18 16:20:35','<p><br></p><div class=\"simditor-image\" contenteditable=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"width: 387px; height: 240.327px;\"><img src=\"http://www.yf-st.com/showImage/1460967835303\" width=\"387\" height=\"240.327\" data-origin-src=\"http://www.yf-st.com/showImage/1460967835303\" data-origin-name=\"图片\" data-origin-size=\"1000,621\">\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle bottom\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right-bottom\"></div>\n</div><p> 2015年最后一天，逸丰生态园举办了一天的冬季趣味运动会，内容有迷你马拉松、猜字谜、萝卜蹲、拔河等项目，员工们参与踊跃，力争上游，体现了团结、友爱、争先的团队精神，始终洋溢着一派欢乐祥和、奋勇向上的氛围。林伟波董事长、袁巧琳副总经理全程参与，并为优胜者颁奖。<br></p><div class=\"simditor-image\" contenteditable=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"width: 387px; height: 240.327px;\"><img src=\"http://www.yf-st.com/showImage/1460968522176\" width=\"387\" height=\"240.327\" data-origin-src=\"http://www.yf-st.com/showImage/1460968522176\" data-origin-name=\"图片\" data-origin-size=\"1000,621\">\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle bottom\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right-bottom\"></div>\n</div><div class=\"simditor-image\" contenteditable=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"width: 387px; height: 240.327px;\"><img src=\"http://www.yf-st.com/showImage/1460968555316\" width=\"387\" height=\"240.327\" data-origin-src=\"http://www.yf-st.com/showImage/1460968555316\" data-origin-name=\"图片\" data-origin-size=\"1000,621\">\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle bottom\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right-bottom\"></div>\n</div><p>  10时许，逸丰生态冬季趣味运动会正式开始，首先举行了升旗仪式，员工们仰望着国旗和公司旗冉冉升起，一股爱国爱企业暖流由然而生。随后开始的迷你马拉松几乎吸引了全体逸丰人参与，最大的参与者年龄已达65岁，最后，种植部的路寅发获得男子第一名，女子第一名被园区销售部的杨紫薇夺得。<br></p><div class=\"simditor-image\" contenteditable=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"width: 387px; height: 240.327px;\"><img src=\"http://www.yf-st.com/showImage/1460968587160\" width=\"387\" height=\"240.327\" data-origin-src=\"http://www.yf-st.com/showImage/1460968587160\" data-origin-name=\"图片\" data-origin-size=\"1000,621\">\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle bottom\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right-bottom\"></div>\n</div><div class=\"simditor-image\" contenteditable=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"width: 387px; height: 240.327px;\"><img src=\"http://www.yf-st.com/showImage/1460968658597\" width=\"387\" height=\"240.327\" data-origin-src=\"http://www.yf-st.com/showImage/1460968658597\" data-origin-name=\"图片\" data-origin-size=\"1000,621\">\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle bottom\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right-bottom\"></div>\n</div><p> 中午，全体逸丰人在石斛煮意餐厅进行了午餐，过后，趣味运动会又开始了新的项目，猜字谜、萝卜蹲、男女运球、拔河即让人忍俊不止，又让人欲罢不能，不争得胜利绝不善罢甘休的劲头彰显其中，体现了逸丰人奋勇争先的豪情。<br></p><div class=\"simditor-image\" contenteditable=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"width: 387px; height: 240.327px;\"><img src=\"http://www.yf-st.com/showImage/1460968802549\" width=\"387\" height=\"240.327\" data-origin-src=\"http://www.yf-st.com/showImage/1460968802549\" data-origin-name=\"图片\" data-origin-size=\"1000,621\">\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle bottom\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right-bottom\"></div>\n</div><p><br></p><p> 趣味运动会结束后，林伟波董事长发表重要讲话，对2015年工作表示满意，感谢全体员工的辛勤付出，对2016年工作充满了希望和憧憬。最后，他的话掷地有声，犹如新年寄语“认识我的人我会带给他健康，跟随我的人我会给他幸福！”——掌声赞叹声回响在生态园区……犹如启航的号角，引领逸丰人向前向前！<br></p>','2015年最后一天，逸丰生态园举办了一天的冬季趣味运动会，内容有迷你马拉松、猜字谜、萝卜蹲、拔河等项目，员工们参与踊跃，力争上游，体现了团结、友爱、争先的团队精神，始终洋溢着一派欢乐祥和、奋勇向上的氛围。林伟波董事长、袁巧琳副总经理全程参与，并为优胜者颁奖。'),(24,'生态养生园','【儿童游乐园】','',NULL,'1461137877521','1461915163524,1461992695511,1461992866667,1461992920088,1461992926385',NULL,'2016-04-20 15:30:53','<h1><b style=\"line-height: 1.1; background-color: transparent;\">逸丰农业生态园-儿童游乐园 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</b><br></h1><h1><b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</b></h1><h1><br><b><div class=\"simditor-image\" contenteditable=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"width: 790px; height: 494px;\"><img src=\"http://yf-st.com/showImage/1461992866667\" width=\"790\" height=\"494\" data-origin-src=\"http://yf-st.com/showImage/1461992866667\" data-origin-name=\"图片\" data-origin-size=\"790,494\">\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle bottom\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right-bottom\"></div>\n</div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</b><b style=\"line-height: 1.1; background-color: transparent;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</b></h1><p>带孩子出来游玩，游乐园是最能引起孩子兴趣的。天真无邪的他们，与父母的欢乐回忆，多半发生在游乐园、动物园。想给孩子一个美好的童年，不妨多带他们来逸丰生态养生园走走。</p><p><br></p><div class=\"simditor-image\" contenteditable=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"width: 790px; height: 494px;\"><img src=\"http://yf-st.com/showImage/1461992695511\" width=\"790\" height=\"494\" data-origin-src=\"http://yf-st.com/showImage/1461992695511\" data-origin-name=\"图片\" data-origin-size=\"790,494\">\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle bottom\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right-bottom\"></div>\n</div><p><br></p><p>逸丰生态养生园儿童游乐园，是广东逸丰生态实业有限公司为孩子们打造的一块乐土。目前逸丰生态养生园已有小规模的儿童游乐场所，全新游乐园正在筹备建设中。</p><p><br></p><div class=\"simditor-image\" contenteditable=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"width: 790px; height: 494px;\"><img src=\"http://yf-st.com/showImage/1461992920088\" width=\"790\" height=\"494\" data-origin-src=\"http://yf-st.com/showImage/1461992920088\" data-origin-name=\"图片\" data-origin-size=\"790,494\">\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle bottom\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right-bottom\"></div>\n</div><p><br></p><p>规划建设的儿童游乐园以“童趣·好玩·益智”为主题，设计理念借鉴国内外众多著名儿童游乐项目，力求从学习、发展、玩耍三大方向，为天真无邪的孩子打造一片欢乐天地，同时给他们留下美好难忘的童年回忆。<span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">儿童游乐园针对不同年龄层配备丰富的游乐设施，旨在发展孩子自身的能力和兴趣。</span></p><p><br></p><div class=\"simditor-image\" contenteditable=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"width: 790px; height: 494px;\"><img src=\"http://yf-st.com/showImage/1461992838370\" width=\"790\" height=\"494\" data-origin-src=\"http://yf-st.com/showImage/1461992838370\" data-origin-name=\"图片\" data-origin-size=\"790,494\">\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle bottom\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right-bottom\"></div>\n</div><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>','带孩子出来游玩，游乐园是最能引起孩子兴趣的。天真无邪的他们，与父母的欢乐回忆，多半发生在游乐园、动物园。所以，想给孩\n\n子一个美好的童年，不妨多带他们来逸丰生态养生园走走。'),(25,'生态养生园','【国学大道】','',NULL,'1461992527606','1461992321856,1461992398715,1461992521512',NULL,'2016-04-20 15:59:56','<h1><b>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<b></b></b></h1><h1><b>逸丰农业生态园-国学大道</b></h1><div><br></div><p><b>传承中华文明，弘扬五千年文化精髓</b></p><p><b><br></b></p><div class=\"simditor-image\" contenteditable=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"width: 834px; height: 556px;\"><img src=\"http://yf-st.com/showImage/1461992521512\" width=\"834\" height=\"556\" data-origin-src=\"http://yf-st.com/showImage/1461992521512\" data-origin-name=\"图片\" data-origin-size=\"834,556\">\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle bottom\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right-bottom\"></div>\n</div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;国学，国家之文学，一般来说，是指以儒学为主体的中华传统文化与学术。逸丰生态养生园国学大道，传承中华文明，弘扬</p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">五</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">千年文</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">化精髓，是园内一道亮丽的风景线。国学大道注重文化内涵的打造：大道两旁有40个国学知识宣传栏，从论语、道德</span><br></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">经，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">再</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">到养生知识的</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">传播，无不重点宣扬“修身·养性·健康”。如果放慢脚步，用心感受中华传统文化的魅力，看似不长的国学大</span><br></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">道，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">也足够</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">你走上一个多小时。</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">如果走累，还可以坐在休闲椅上歇歇脚，或与亲朋好友谈笑风生。</span><br></p><p>&nbsp;</p><div class=\"simditor-image\" contenteditable=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"width: 838px; height: 559px;\"><img src=\"http://yf-st.com/showImage/1461914443104\" width=\"838\" height=\"559\" data-origin-src=\"http://yf-st.com/showImage/1461914443104\" data-origin-name=\"图片\" data-origin-size=\"838,559\">\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle bottom\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right-bottom\"></div>\n</div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>大道的棚顶，波浪式悬挂着鲜红的绸布，除了养眼，寓意传统、喜庆、吉祥外，还起到很好<span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">的遮阴效果。露天式结构，亲近</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">自</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">然，强</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">烈的阳光透过绸布，转化成弱光，洋洋洒洒；微风</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">从四面八方吹来，沁人心脾。每相隔同等距离，便有藤类植物萦绕铁</span><br></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">柱而</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">上，红绿相</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">映，别</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">样风情。</span><br></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\"><br></span></p><p>《道德经》言：上善若水。水善利万物而不争，居众人之所恶，故几于道。居善地，心善渊，<span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">与善仁，言善信，政善治，事</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">善能，动</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">善时。夫唯不争，故无尤。</span><br></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\"><br></span></p><p>《论语》中，子曰：“吾十有五而志于学，三十而立，四十而不惑，五十而知天命，六十而<span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">耳顺，七十而从心所欲，不逾矩。”</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\"><br></span></p><div class=\"simditor-image\" contenteditable=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"width: 834px; height: 556px;\"><img src=\"http://yf-st.com/showImage/1461992321856\" width=\"834\" height=\"556\" data-origin-src=\"http://yf-st.com/showImage/1461992321856\" data-origin-name=\"图片\" data-origin-size=\"834,556\">\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle bottom\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right-bottom\"></div>\n</div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>现代社会的很多人因为各种各样的事而心浮气躁，通过对国学的学习和实践可以修身养性，中华民族是一个以和为贵的民</p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">族，我们的</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">老祖先认为，一个完整的生命是和谐的，包括与自身、家庭、社会、自然、哲学等诸多方面的和谐，这样的和谐思</span><br></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">想包含在各类经典作品</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">里。千年国学的智慧沉淀，用简洁的语言告诉我们人生财富的获取根本，财之本为德。</span><br></p><div class=\"simditor-image\" contenteditable=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"width: 205px; height: 154px;\">\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle bottom\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right-bottom\"></div>\n</div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><b><br></b></p>','国学，国家之文学，一般来说，是指以儒学为主体的中华传统文化与学术。逸丰生态养生园国学大道，传承中华文明，弘扬五千年文化精髓，是园内一道亮丽的风景线。国学大道注重文化内涵的打造：大道两旁有40个国学知识宣传栏，从论语、道德经，再到养生知识的传播，无不重点宣扬“修身·养性·健康”。如果放慢脚步，用心感受中华传统文化的魅力，看似不长的国学大道，也足够你走上一个多小时。如果走累，还可以坐在休闲椅上歇歇脚，或与亲朋好友谈笑风生。'),(26,'生态养生园','【逸丰生态养生园动物园简介】','珍稀',NULL,'1461140839638','1461908864619,1461908867588,1461908873869,1461908883775,1461908889494,1462586034606',NULL,'2016-04-20 16:13:08','<p><br></p><h1>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<br></h1><h1>逸丰生态养生园-珍稀动物园</h1><div><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.1; background-color: transparent;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.1; background-color: transparent;\">走进动物世界</span></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \'Open Sans\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.1; background-color: transparent;\"><br></span></div><div><div class=\"simditor-image\" contenteditable=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"width: 968px; height: 605px;\"><img src=\"http://yf-st.com/showImage/1461908873869\" width=\"968\" height=\"605\" data-origin-src=\"http://yf-st.com/showImage/1461908873869\" data-origin-name=\"图片\" data-origin-size=\"1000,625\">\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle bottom\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right-bottom\"></div>\n</div><br></div><p>动物园是逸丰生态养生园内的又一大手笔，不仅丰富了园区的景点建设，也让游客在放松身心的同时又多了一个游玩的</p><p>好去处！每一<span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">位入园的游客，都可以免费参观我们的动物园。</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\"><br></span></p><div class=\"simditor-image\" contenteditable=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"width: 968px; height: 605px;\"><img src=\"http://yf-st.com/showImage/1461908867588\" width=\"968\" height=\"605\" data-origin-src=\"http://yf-st.com/showImage/1461908867588\" data-origin-name=\"图片\" data-origin-size=\"1000,625\">\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle bottom\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right-bottom\"></div>\n</div><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">&nbsp;动物园位于逸丰生态养生园大门的东北方向，从正门进入后，可往左沿着园区水泥道直走即到，也可以穿过石斛煮意餐</span><br></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">厅到达。动物</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">园内建有三个饲养区，展览动物数十种，包括珠海难得一见的骆驼、矮马、驼羊、锦鸡、鸳鸯等。旅游高峰期，</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">每天接待游客5000多人</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">次，是逸丰生态养生园最受欢迎的景观之一。</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><b><b>骆驼</b><br></b></p><p><b><b><br></b></b></p><div class=\"simditor-image\" contenteditable=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"width: 968px; height: 605px;\"><img src=\"http://yf-st.com/showImage/1461908864619\" width=\"968\" height=\"605\" data-origin-src=\"http://yf-st.com/showImage/1461908864619\" data-origin-name=\"图片\" data-origin-size=\"1000,625\">\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle bottom\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right-bottom\"></div>\n</div><p><br></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">&nbsp;骆驼有着“沙漠之舟”的美称，头较小，颈粗长，弯曲如鹅颈。躯体高大，体毛褐色。极能忍饥耐渴。骆驼可以在没有水的</span><br></p><p>条件下生存3<span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">周，没有食物可生存一个月之久。</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\"><br></span></p><p><b>驼羊</b><br></p><p><b><br></b></p><div class=\"simditor-image selected\" contenteditable=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"width: 968px; height: 606.33px;\"><img src=\"http://yf-st.com/showImage/1462586034606\" width=\"968\" height=\"606.3296703296703\" data-origin-src=\"http://yf-st.com/showImage/1462586034606\" data-origin-name=\"图片\" data-origin-size=\"1001,627\">\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle bottom\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right-bottom\"></div>\n</div><p><br></p><p>驼羊又叫“草泥马”，曾分布在南美的西部和南部，是南美四种骆驼形动物中最有名的一种，早在1000多年前被驯化，是西半</p><p>球人驯化<span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">成驮兽的唯一一种动物。</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">驼羊长相呆萌，性情机警，视觉、听觉、嗅觉均很敏锐，奔跑速度也很快，每小时可达55公里。</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\"><br></span></p><p><b>锦鸡</b><br></p><p><b><br></b></p><div class=\"simditor-image\" contenteditable=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"width: 968px; height: 605px;\"><img src=\"http://yf-st.com/showImage/1461908883775\" width=\"968\" height=\"605\" data-origin-src=\"http://yf-st.com/showImage/1461908883775\" data-origin-name=\"图片\" data-origin-size=\"1000,625\">\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle bottom\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right-bottom\"></div>\n</div><p><br></p><p>锦鸡是一种雉科动物，是学名白腹锦鸡、红腹锦鸡的统称。分布在陕西(商洛)西藏、四川、贵州、云南、广西等地，属国</p><p>家二级保护<span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">动物。锦鸡一般是成对生活的，雌鸡每窝产卵5~9枚，浅黄褐色或乳白色，光滑无斑，由雄鸡雌鸡轮流孵化，孵卵</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">期为21天。</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\"><br></span></p><p><b style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\"><b>鸳鸯</b></b><br></p><p><b><b><br></b></b></p><div class=\"simditor-image\" contenteditable=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"width: 968px; height: 605px;\"><img src=\"http://yf-st.com/showImage/1461908889494\" width=\"968\" height=\"605\" data-origin-src=\"http://yf-st.com/showImage/1461908889494\" data-origin-name=\"图片\" data-origin-size=\"1000,625\">\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle bottom\"></div>\n  <div class=\"simditor-image-resize-handle right-bottom\"></div>\n</div><p><br></p><p>鸳鸯为中国著名的观赏鸟类，之所以被看成爱情的象征，因为人们见到的鸳鸯都是出双入对的。作为经常出现在古代汉族</p><p>神话传说和<span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">文学作品中的鸟类。人们常用鸳鸯来比喻男女之间的爱情。</span></p><p>在小小动物世界，与温顺可爱的他们零距离接触，用不同的语言体系对话，乐趣无穷。尤其适合想满足孩子对动物世界的幻想</p><p>的家庭。</p><p><br></p>','动物园是逸丰生态养生园内的又一大手笔，不仅丰富了园区的景点建设，也让游客在放松身心的同时又多了一个游玩的好去处！每一\n\n位入园的游客，都可以免费参观我们的动物园。'),(27,'生态养生园','逸丰生态养生园—花海主题旅游景点',NULL,NULL,'1462586023090','1461909563101,1461909567695,1461909573601,1461909579882',NULL,'2016-04-20 16:41:57','<h1><br></h1><div><br></div><h1>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br></h1><h1>&nbsp;逸丰生态养生园—花海主题旅游景点</h1><div><br></div><div><br></div><p>逸丰生态养生园之花海主题旅游景点位于逸丰生态养生园西北方向，占地面积超百亩，是广<span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">东珠海</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">最</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">大，最</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">热门的旅游景点之一。因为花开四季，花卉品种名贵且丰富，备受游客青睐。</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">四季花海，缤纷多彩。百亩面积的广阔视野，数百种名贵花卉璀璨盛放，沿着观光小道，一</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">路与“国泰”郁金香、风信子、百合、格桑花……打招呼、自拍留影，都是一件奇趣无比的</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">乐事。阳光明媚，芳香四溢，游客在花海里徜徉，乐不思蜀。如果游客从高空往下看，将会</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">看到置身花海的观光石板小道，竟然连接成一个迈步行走的人型。</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">四季花海</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">每季都有顺应时节的花品竞相绽放</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">在微风中摇曳</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">随时准备着与游客相遇</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; backgrou